node.text: The Bailsmen bring some love back into the house ❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dante NYC in Dante West Village. May be an image of food and drink.

node.text:
Crowd favorite 😍

SPICY FRESCA
mezcal verde. el tequileno blanco. galliano. fluffy grapefruit & soda. agave. smoked jalapeno. aleppo salt 

@dantewestvillage @lindenpride 
📸: @giadapaoloni

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dante NYC in Dante West Village with @rodrigooleme, @nathaliehudson, @giadapaoloni, @rileysheehey, and @mr.calvados. May be an image of drink.

node.text:
Is there anything better than drinking martinis in the afternoon? We’ve been working a curated menu of classics and house interpretations of signature martinis as part of our #MartiniHour. All available, all the time. But between 3pm and 5pm - they’re only $10!

Join us for our #MartiniHour at @dantewestvillage 🍸

We’re also donating $1 from each martini sold during #MartiniHour to our dear friends at @godslovenyc ❤️

📸: @giadapaoloni 
👩🏼‍🎨: @rileysheehey

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dante NYC in Dante with @carlos_iriz, @rodrigooleme, @akhada_, @lindenpride, @gigitemprano, @thirsty, @mr.calvados, and @prcocktailweek. May be an image of drink and indoor.

May be an image of indoor and text that says '2013 La Factoría COCHUE ARTESANAL COMES TO DANTE NEW YORK CITY AUGUST 16TH TO 18TH 2PM 6PM'.

node.text:
Dante is thrilled to announce our first residency of 2021, hosting our dear friends from Puerto Rico’s legendary cocktail bar @lafactoriapr 🇵🇷❤️. 

Factoría bartenders Carlos Irizarry and Gigi Temprano will join Dante’s Head Bartender Bar Eloy Pacheco to bring local Caribbean flavors in a selection of tropical rum-based cocktails from @bacardiusa . Cuban performer Chino Ponds will play a variety of Latin music for all three days of the pop-up, from 2:00pm daily.

$2 from each cocktail sold will be donated directly to @prcocktailweek Tip Jar, an emergency fund established to help support the local Puerto Rican hospitality industry impacted by the closures of bars and restaurants due to the COVID-19 pandemic.

Monday Aug 16 through Wednesday Aug 18 from 3pm til 6pm during BCB at Caffe Dante, Macdougal street.

Reservations available through RESY. We can’t wait to host you ❤️

node.text:
We’re thrilled to announce Dante West Village will open daily for breakfast from 10am, starting today☀️

It’s been an incredibly challenging 12 months since we opened @dantewestvillage . A project we fought through construction delays, a cancelled opening due to COVID, followed by a myriad of restrictions due to the pandemic. 

We’ve grown our Dante family during that time, creating a special second location to our flagship Caffe Dante. We’re incredibly grateful to our community and all the staff who have helped us along this journey. We can’t wait to serve you ❤️
